      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2482448-the-cellist-of-sarajevo">Quotes from The Cellist of Sa...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;A weapon does not decide whether or not to kill. A weapon is a manifestation of a decision that has already been made.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
